com.sun.star.uno

Interface IMapping

  • Deprecated. 
    As of UDK 3.2, this interface is deprecated, without offering a replacement.

    @Deprecated
public interface IMapping
    With a mapping objects can be mapped from one environment to another.

    This interface exists for compatibility with the binary UNO API.

    See Also:
